  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9c\u0baa\u0b95\u0bcd\u0bb7\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0baa\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a \u0baa\u0baf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0ba4\u0bc1 - \u0b9a\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Shadow government of Rajapaksas has used state terror on disarmament workers - Sajid",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "The shadow government of the Rajapaksas has used state terror to launch brutal attacks on unarmed protesters.",
        "Leader of the Opposition Sajith Premadasa insisted that those involved in these attacks should undergo independent investigations and be brought before the law and urged the President to clarify this to the people of the country.",
        "He said this at a press conference held on Friday (22) at the Office of the Leader of the Opposition in Colombo.",
        "The shadow government of the Rajapaksas has used state terrorism to launch brutal attacks on unarmed demonstrators. We hoped that with the appointment of the new President, there would be better development in the country.",
        "But the first act of the new president is state terror and brutal violence. Due to this, massive attacks have been carried out on unarmed civilians, women, disabled soldiers and many others.",
        "We strongly condemn these attacks on behalf of all opposition parties. It is the responsibility of this government to conduct independent investigations and bring to justice those responsible for these heinous attacks.",
        "We also inform that the President cannot withdraw from this responsibility. He should be held responsible for this.",
        "Who authorized these brutal attacks? With whose cooperation was this state terrorism staged?",
        "We want to ask the government if attacking local and foreign journalists is the strategy of this government to develop the tourism industry. Foreign ambassadors have condemned this.",
        "International cooperation is essential to rebuilding a failing economy. Similarly, human rights should be protected. And its implementation is essential.",
        "We want to inform the government that the future of the country is democracy. Within this democracy the basic rights of the people should be guaranteed. People should be given the opportunity to exercise these rights without violence.",
        "Similarly, people should maintain peace while exercising these rights without causing damage to state and public property. These are the ideologies that should be implemented in democracies.",
        "We also emphasize that the President should clarify this to the country and the people of the country. We also know that they have announced that they are going to clean up and hand over the place where the demonstration took place; The government also knows.",
        "However, we would like to ask the President why this attack was carried out through the military. We reiterate that you should not attempt to act violently or in a manner that is blatantly harassing. He said that we will gather lakhs of people against these and take to the streets and fight to protect democracy."
      ],
